^B@2^*BMM: ^*N|cp||at|In this auction there is only one unbid major suit—spades—so that is what the suit responder's Negative Double promises. Responder needs about 8+ points to double here. As you note, responder has diamond length in this example—he doesn't have to for a double—and his double says nothing about diamonds.|
