You are sitting South and the bidding goes as is shown above.|
pg| ***** 32 ***** |


NT||lb|*bWhat would you bid?^^2S|nt|
^b@2Here you have 2@S as a limit raise cue bid if you do not distinguish a 4-card support from a 3-card support.|mb|2s|
